    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034960/extras/5ebcbc03852287039e4f7e9bc400b9c3.poster.avif?t=1764717678\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034960/extras/5ebcbc03852287039e4f7e9bc400b9c3.webm?t=1764717678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034960/extras/5ebcbc03852287039e4f7e9bc400b9c3.mp4?t=1764717678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>A Strategic, Turn-Based Puzzle Game.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Minimalistic, challenging and telegraphed</strong> gameplay that is easy to pick up.<br></li><li> <strong>Hand-crafted levels</strong> and a variety of unique tile types.<br></li><li> <strong>Tactile and explosive</strong>, with hand drawn pixel art and an ominous soundtrack.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034960/extras/e817463aa23b1c0cee1f3248adc2e116.poster.avif?t=1764717678\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034960/extras/e817463aa23b1c0cee1f3248adc2e116.webm?t=1764717678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034960/extras/e817463aa23b1c0cee1f3248adc2e116.mp4?t=1764717678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ABOUT XENOSPORE</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>The Xenospore spreads and mutates</strong> predictably each turn.<br></li><li> <strong>Destroy tiles</strong> to isolate cities from the Xenospore fungus.<br></li><li> <strong>Cleanse infected cities </strong> before they are consumed.<br></li><li> <strong>Activate technology tiles</strong> to protect cities.<br></li><li> <strong>Isolate volatile facilities</strong> before they explode or mutate.<br></li><li> <strong>You can only act upon tile groups</strong> of the same type.<br></li><li> <strong>Outsmart the infection</strong> by leveraging its spread to eradicate larger areas.</li></ul>",
